snippet.title: Wreckfest - Nintendo Switch Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
No plumbers, no princesses, only carnage. Wreckfest is coming to Nintendo Switch Fall 2021!

Crash couches, school busses and toilets while you’re on the couch, school bus or toilet! Are you ready to customize your vehicles, hit the race track and wreck your competition wherever you go?

- Links & Info -
Website: https://order.wreckfestgame.com
Discord: https://discord.gg/wreckfest

- Our Socials -
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/THQNordic
Twitter: https://twitter.com/THQNordic
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/wreckfestofficial
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/thqnordic
